<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:07:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列选择英国法律专家在国际法院种族灭绝案中代表以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-chooses-british-legal-expert-to-represent-it-in-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-d5e5-d751-ad8d-ffe5b4880000</link><description>以色列法律专家表示，马尔科姆·肖教授必须辩称，以色列实际上遵守了国际法，以色列领导人的极端言论并不反映加沙的官方政策</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-chooses-british-legal-expert-to-represent-it-in-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-d5e5-d751-ad8d-ffe5b4880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，自 10 月 7 日以来失踪的三名以色列人被绑架到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/three-israeli-civilians-missing-since-october-7-were-kidnapped-to-gaza-idf-says/0000018c-d5ee-ddba-abad-d7effb590000</link><description>三名被绑架的以色列人中的两人被确认为来自特拉维夫的 42 岁哈南·亚布隆卡 (Hanan Yablonka) 和 28 岁的伊丹·什蒂维 (Idan Shtivi)</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:45:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/three-israeli-civilians-missing-since-october-7-were-kidnapped-to-gaza-idf-says/0000018c-d5ee-ddba-abad-d7effb590000</guid></item><item><title>你不会通过否认哈马斯强奸以色列人来解放巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-04/ty-article/.highlight/you-wont-free-palestine-by-denying-hamas-raped-israelis/0000018c-d582-ddba-abad-d7a3d6510000</link><description>你可以拆开每个证人的证词，手摇每一个被剥光尸体的视频，并告诉每个愿意听的人，哈马斯不会这样做。但这不会抹去受害者在最后一刻所遭受的苦难，也不会解放巴勒斯坦</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-04/ty-article/.highlight/you-wont-free-palestine-by-denying-hamas-raped-israelis/0000018c-d582-ddba-abad-d7a3d6510000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸难民营，审问数百名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-west-bank-refugee-camp-interrogates-hundreds-of-palestinians/0000018c-d583-ddba-abad-d7a3b2a70000</link><description>这是以色列国防军在努尔沙姆斯难民营进行的最长的行动，自战争开始以来，该难民营的军事活动不断增加。据报道，两名以色列士兵和几名巴勒斯坦人在行动中受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:32:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-raids-west-bank-refugee-camp-interrogates-hundreds-of-palestinians/0000018c-d583-ddba-abad-d7a3b2a70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：巴勒斯坦人将对战后加沙负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-palestinian-players-to-be-responsible-for-gaza-after-war/0000018c-d59a-ddba-abad-d7bbc7660000</link><description>以色列国防部长约夫·加兰特在以色列战时内阁就巴勒斯坦飞地计划进行首次讨论之前表示，“战争目标实现后，以色列将不会在加沙地带出现任何民事存在”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-palestinian-players-to-be-responsible-for-gaza-after-war/0000018c-d59a-ddba-abad-d7bbc7660000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列对加沙的破坏中，出现了一种新的反人类罪：杀戮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/amid-israeli-destruction-in-gaza-a-new-crime-against-humanity-emerges-domicide/0000018c-d585-d751-ad8d-ffa5965e0000</link><description>以色列在加沙的猛烈轰炸行动的观察者们引用了“杀戮”一词。蓄意、系统地破坏房屋和基本基础设施很快就会在法律上被定义为反人类罪——以色列将何去何从？</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/amid-israeli-destruction-in-gaza-a-new-crime-against-humanity-emerges-domicide/0000018c-d585-d751-ad8d-ffa5965e0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗核武器、10 月 7 日和内塔尼亚胡：鲁莽的遗产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/irans-nukes-october-7-and-netanyahu-a-reckless-legacy/0000018c-d4a9-d4e1-ad8f-fcb9c7000000</link><description>正如以色列总理拒绝为导致哈马斯屠杀的鲁莽行为承担责任一样，他也拒绝为放弃他自己视为毕生使命的问题承担责任。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/irans-nukes-october-7-and-netanyahu-a-reckless-legacy/0000018c-d4a9-d4e1-ad8f-fcb9c7000000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院命令政府部长放弃解雇以色列邮政主席</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/supreme-court-orders-government-ministers-to-abandon-israel-post-chairman-firing/0000018c-d4e9-daf6-a5df-d7fd6be90000</link><description>两名利库德集团议员坚持在战争期间解雇以色列邮政主席米沙尔·瓦克宁，尽管有证据表明邮政服务在他的指挥下正在改善。瓦克宁和《华盛顿邮报》认为，推翻他的企图是政治性的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:18:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/supreme-court-orders-government-ministers-to-abandon-israel-post-chairman-firing/0000018c-d4e9-daf6-a5df-d7fd6be90000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院指控以色列犯有种族灭绝罪：请愿书、先例和惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-at-the-icj-petition-precedents-and-punishment/0000018c-d449-ddba-abad-d6e91a480000</link><description>南非为何向海牙国际法院提交针对以色列在加沙行为的请愿书？为什么以色列有兴趣配合诉讼程序？可能的结果是什么？</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-at-the-icj-petition-precedents-and-punishment/0000018c-d449-ddba-abad-d6e91a480000</guid></item><item><title>格罗斯曼、齐泽克等公众人物签署反对“巴勒斯坦人和以色列人非人化”的信</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/public-figures-sign-letter-against-the-dehumanization-of-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018c-d47c-ddba-abad-d6fdf7d20000</link><description>“亲人类阵营联盟”反对“10月7日犯下的暴行”，也反对将所有加沙人与哈马斯等同起来，“哈马斯利用哈马斯为不分青红皂白的杀戮和拒绝人道主义援助合理化”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/public-figures-sign-letter-against-the-dehumanization-of-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018c-d47c-ddba-abad-d6fdf7d20000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质重返 10 月 7 日改变他们生活的现场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-return-to-the-scenes-that-changed-their-lives-on-october-7/0000018c-d4aa-d4e1-ad8f-fcbb05d10000</link><description>在三个月前被哈马斯摧毁的贝埃里基布兹这次不寻常的旅行中，游客也是主要受害者：“这是我自 10 月 7 日以来第一次来到贝埃里。经历了这一切之后我很难再来这里”我们已经经历过&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 13:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-return-to-the-scenes-that-changed-their-lives-on-october-7/0000018c-d4aa-d4e1-ad8f-fcbb05d10000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院的加沙种族灭绝案有一个不知情的盟友：以色列政客</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/gaza-genocide-case-at-the-icj-has-an-unwitting-ally-israeli-politicians/0000018c-d479-d4e1-ad8f-fcf93ae90000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡本可以要求他的部长们闭嘴，停止说有关加沙的蠢话。相反，他忽视甚至鼓励他们。他欢迎南非向国际法院提出的轻率请求，因为这证明了他的“世界反对我们，这不是我的错”的说法是正确的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 13:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/gaza-genocide-case-at-the-icj-has-an-unwitting-ally-israeli-politicians/0000018c-d479-d4e1-ad8f-fcf93ae90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日袭击事件以来，自杀率并未出现飙升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/no-spike-in-suicide-rates-since-oct-7-attack-israeli-health-ministry-says/0000018c-d404-daf6-a5df-d77c0d980000</link><description>根据法医研究所收集的部分数据，卫生部的声明显示，有迹象表明，过去三个月的自杀人数甚至低于平时。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 12:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/no-spike-in-suicide-rates-since-oct-7-attack-israeli-health-ministry-says/0000018c-d404-daf6-a5df-d77c0d980000</guid></item><item><title>待在室内：希伯伦居民面临着前所未有的限制，无法离开家园或社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hebron-residents-face-restrictions-like-never-before-unable-to-even-leave-their-homes/0000018c-d3db-daf6-a5df-d7ff8aab0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，以色列实施的限制导致居住在约旦河西岸城市以色列控制地区的希伯伦居民无法前往工作场所，甚至无法购买食物。军队声称希伯伦没有宵禁，但现实却并非如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 12:20:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hebron-residents-face-restrictions-like-never-before-unable-to-even-leave-their-homes/0000018c-d3db-daf6-a5df-d7ff8aab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列杂志刊登漫画，描绘前最高法院院长在加沙踩士兵背</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-magazine-runs-cartoon-depicting-ex-top-court-president-stepping-on-soldiers-back/0000018c-d3fc-d4e1-ad8f-fffda54e0000</link><description>该杂志主要由宗教犹太复国主义读者阅读，收到了法院管理法律顾问的一封措辞强硬的信，认为这可能相当于“煽动暴力”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 11:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-magazine-runs-cartoon-depicting-ex-top-court-president-stepping-on-soldiers-back/0000018c-d3fc-d4e1-ad8f-fffda54e0000</guid></item><item><title>“对儿童来说更加困难”：严重的饥饿正在加沙蔓延。来自人类灾难的四种声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/severe-hunger-is-spreading-in-gaza-four-voices-from-a-human-catastrophe/0000018c-d3da-d4e1-ad8f-fffbf0800000</link><description>加沙不可能的现实：营养不良而无法母乳喂养的母亲在爆炸的威胁下寻找食物，援助组织在压力下崩溃</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/severe-hunger-is-spreading-in-gaza-four-voices-from-a-human-catastrophe/0000018c-d3da-d4e1-ad8f-fffbf0800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡因偏执而制定的法律即将被扔进历史的垃圾箱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-paranoia-induced-law-is-on-its-way-to-historys-dumpster/0000018c-d39f-daf6-a5df-d7ff6e7f0000</link><description>总检察长将保留宣布总理内塔尼亚胡不适合任职的能力，但高等法院法官没有澄清她在什么情况下可以这样做。 10 月 7 日之后以色列内塔尼亚胡政府的公众舆论表明她似乎不太可能会这样做</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:35:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-paranoia-induced-law-is-on-its-way-to-historys-dumpster/0000018c-d39f-daf6-a5df-d7ff6e7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人应该为了自己的利益而停止战争，即使不是为了加沙的利益。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-should-want-to-stop-the-war-for-their-own-sake-if-not-for-gazas/0000018c-d37e-ddba-abad-d3ff951d0000</link><description>精神卫生服务不堪重负，教育系统半运转不灵，经济衰退，企业倒闭，枪支事故令人不安，犯罪率上升。即使大多数以色列人不会为了加沙人而反对战争，他们也最好开始考虑战争给自己的生活带来的巨大损失</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 09:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-should-want-to-stop-the-war-for-their-own-sake-if-not-for-gazas/0000018c-d37e-ddba-abad-d3ff951d0000</guid></item><item><title>高等法院的新裁决：内塔尼亚胡家族所有恐惧的总和</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/high-courts-new-ruling-the-sum-of-all-fears-for-netanyahu-family/0000018c-d109-ddba-abad-d3a9fabc0000</link><description>在阻止废除合理性标准两天后，以色列最高法院还废除了旨在剥夺总检察长宣布总理不适合任职的法律选择的法律。至少在战争期间，内塔尼亚胡计划的反对以色列民主的政变已经因法官席上的自由派多数而停止</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/high-courts-new-ruling-the-sum-of-all-fears-for-netanyahu-family/0000018c-d109-ddba-abad-d3a9fabc0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国压力下，以色列考虑开放埃雷兹过境点以提供加沙人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/under-u-s-pressure-israel-weighs-opening-erez-crossing-for-gaza-humanitarian-aid/0000018c-d0f5-daf6-a5df-d7fd7e190000</link><description>这将直接向加沙北部的居民提供援助，该地区获得的援助远不如南部那么多。以色列国防军控制了加沙北部的大部分地区，并且可以确保哈马斯无法劫持援助卡车并自行保留物资，这与南部地区不同。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 04:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/under-u-s-pressure-israel-weighs-opening-erez-crossing-for-gaza-humanitarian-aid/0000018c-d0f5-daf6-a5df-d7fd7e190000</guid></item></channel></rss>